values: Today was alrite...went to Carter Caves with the german students....Blah!...it sucked...then i took some of them to the mall..,they are so funny...all i have learned since they were here is dirty stuf..which is just what i need to know..NOt...then i hung out with Travis = ) * i think things are actually going to work for me this time...im just happy...

Hey Im at school...I hadnt undated in forever cuz i never have time. I work like everyday...and when im not im sleepin or busy...im so worn out with everything rite now...its just too much for me...but im happy finally...ive let myself get away from everything that made me depressed...i was just so selfish for a while...but i am just glad ive made it past this...but school is okay now...everyone seems to be getting along with everyone...no drama = sweetness! but today Jana is gone ( german exchange student ) so i guess i can be alone...im gonna just hang out with travis... = )...but i guess that im done...ill try to start updating more often...
later guys!

Last night i stayed with Catrina...we had fun...except for the not goin to bed until 6 o clock part...im sooo tired..we ate like 5 bowls of cereal when we got home.
 Anyways...my life is pretty gay right now...this whole situation thats going on with these "people" sucks really bad...i really dont know how to handle things...but...we went and looked at cars today it was really stressful..Buti guess im just gonna buy the Jetta...its nice but i would rather have that 3000GT ... my dream car...its sooo beautiful...but im too poor..lol...but anyways Im gonna go eat chinese! lata guyz

Your wings are BROKEN and tattered. You are
an angelic spirit who has fallen from grace for
one reason or another - possibly, you made one
tragic mistake that cost you everything. Or
maybe you were blamed for a crime you didn't
commit. In any case, you are faithless and
joyless. You find no happiness, love, or
acceptance in your love or in yourself. Most
days are a burden and you wonder when the
hurting will end. Sweet, beautiful and
sorrowful, you paint a tragic and touching
picture. You are the one that few understand.
Those that do know you are likely to love you
deeply and wish that they could do something to
ease your pain. You are constantly living in
memories of better times and a better world.
You are hard on yourself and self-critical or
self-loathing. Feeling rejected and unloved,
you are sensitive, caring, deep, and despite
your tainted nature, your soul is
breathtakingly beautiful.

*~*~*Claim Your Wings - Pics and Long Answers*~*~*

Its pink and tye-dyed...so no one buy it. i almost bought one and then they said some girl from spring valley had already bought it...so i didnt get it. that would be horrible...i dunno if itll be fun though...i usually hate dances the only one i ever had fun at was this years homecoming...it was cool...too much being social for me though...today is james's dad's birthday im supposed to go but he hasnt called...soo i dunno...Ill probably update later cuz  have nothing else to do
